    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Most importantly the environment is safe for girls and college is near to transportation options like railway station or bus stand",
          "name": "Rupali",
          "course_tag_name": "M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Best laboratories in the area with professionally trained assistants",
          "name": "Rupali",
          "course_tag_name": "M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Teachers in chemistry department are having a great experience in life as well as teaching",
          "name": "Rupali",
          "course_tag_name": "M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Our college support students hobbies and talent",
          "name": "Lakshay",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Park of college is so green. There are flowers of roses in park.",
          "name": "Lakshay",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The teachers are too good , especially from mathematics and chemistry department.",
          "name": "Dinesh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "I took admission in the college in 2018 and from this year , college started its co-ed policy for bachelor courses.",
          "name": "Dinesh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The environment is good. There are trees and lush green in garden.",
          "name": "Dinesh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Disciplined campus was there as it feels like we are in the school One of the best college of Sonipat to pursue Bachelors",
          "name": "Review Ranger",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Campus life was good faculties are of great support Mathematics and computer teachers are of great experience",
          "name": "Review Ranger",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The buildings are much older which should be reconstructed but not in that bad condition",
          "name": "Rupali",
          "course_tag_name": "M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Sometimes nuisance is created due to some non-behaved children and student parties",
          "name": "Rupali",
          "course_tag_name": "M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Our college fund is very low. Canteen food is limited",
          "name": "Lakshay",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "There are no medical rooms in college  for first aid treatment.",
          "name": "Lakshay",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college just started its co-ed policy. So, the number of girls is too less. Around 1:6 ratio for girls to boys.",
          "name": "Dinesh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "College don't provide placement opportunity.",
          "name": "Dinesh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Sports ground is too far from the main campus. That's why students don't go to the ground and avoid sports activities.",
          "name": "Dinesh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Canteen is also in very poor condition and only one canteen is there and no clubs and society in college.",
          "name": "Review Ranger",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Not well equipped labs are in the campus also the labs are not modern at all.",
          "name": "Review Ranger",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "College lacks most of the modern day infrasturcture.",
          "name": "Review Ranger",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        }
      ]
    },
